Tendai Mugabe Senior Reporter Veteran nationalist Cde Naison Khutshwekhaya Ndlovu who died yesterday has been declared a national hero.Zanu-PF secretary for administration Cde Ignatius Chombo has confirmed. Cde Naison K Ndlovu has been declared National Hero by President Cde R.G Mugabe. Burial arrangements will be announced in due course.Cde Ndlovu died at the age of 86.